d<-d %>% filter(age>=18)

## [1] 352   4
m4.3<-
  rethinking::map(alist(
  height~dnorm(mu, sigma),
  mu~beta0+beta1*weight,
  beta0~dnorm(156, 100),
  beta1~dnorm(0, 10),
  sigma ~ dunif(0, 50)
), data=d
)


m_add_age<-
  rethinking::map(alist(
  height~dnorm(mu, sigma),
  mu~beta0+beta1*weight+beta2*age,
  beta0~dnorm(156, 100),
  beta1~dnorm(0, 10),
  beta2~dnorm(0, 10),
  sigma ~ dunif(0, 50)
), data=d
)
